  <brief_title>Heath-related Quality of Life of Diabetic Transmetatarsal Amputees and Below-knee Prosthetic Users</brief_title>
  <official_title>Heath-related Quality of Life of Diabetic Transmetatarsal Amputees and Below-knee Prosthetic Users</official_title>
